levels

Class GameLevel

  • java.lang.Object
    • city.cs.engine.World
      • levels.GameLevel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Level1, Level2, Level3

    public abstract class GameLevel
extends city.cs.engine.World
    An abstract class representing a level in the game. It includes the setup for the player, enemies, collectibles, and the environment. Each level has specific enemies, obstacles, and goals that need to be completed to progress.
    Since:
    1.0

        public GameLevel(Game game)
        Constructs a game level with a reference to the main game object. It initializes the level by adding world components like the ground, enemies, and the player.
        Parameters:
        game - The game controller that manages the levels and transitions.
